Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:53.45,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:16.48,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've overcome your most difficult battle yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably need some time to rest and recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is of the essence, but knowing when to take a break is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you won't get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mr. Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you came home drenched yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! We just bought it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I warm your dinner up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nanako. Have you heard of Neo Featherman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone loves him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Heroes these days are something else, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!{TV announcer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come see for yourself, and get in touch with our products!{TV announcer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! I hear you've been coming home late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's wasabi in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget to wipe it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Halibut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have great taste, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I'll have urchin roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! That was the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how it is! You snooze, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, back to Yu!{hah pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You did, didn't you? You got a girl!{he got 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have solved the case, but watch the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't a girl, what's keeping you out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were you such a tease?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, that was a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that killer was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he was just a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad we caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingerprints were on the victims' clothes, so this case is as good as closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you doubt the one you love, solve the case promptly with the power of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to us!{on tv}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When our eyes lock, a new case starts up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll trail after—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to me!{seriously, she looks like that milky holmes chick}{my thoughts exactly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nana, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mas—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Trailing him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... My nose says to go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Bro's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Just trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need a new stomach for these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, where's Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're all round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly, roly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly, roly-poly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our little secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to the bottom of this today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Yu would make poor Nanako worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gotta admit, he hasn't been hanging out with us lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. He's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on! There's no point thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, we'll help out, so let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty tough without any clues to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd wander very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie took the bus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that bear your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teddie! What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not a suspicious bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't his voice sound off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normally more, uh, hyperactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how he randomly rolls around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why'd he run from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro said he'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it, Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll continue conducting the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know some big words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to solve the mystery today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro was walking with some woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You see, Yuuta isn't really my son.{woman}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Was this your "urgent business"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude! It's even an older woman!{lots of overlaps here}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was in the middle of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho! So {\i1}that's{\i0} Master's type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not the same woman I saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the?!{— perhaps?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't believe it till I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go double check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But we don't really care.{whores}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be embarrassing if he caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came prepared for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this even a disguise?{those glasses are fucking amazing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job for the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Br—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi screwed things up {\i1}again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm stuck here for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I even promised I'd take you to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The case will never be closed if the detective gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't drop the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the investigating to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you doubt the one you love, solve the case promptly with the power of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! How'd they sell out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Some gorgeous foreign boy who spoke all funny-like gobbled it up like you wouldn't believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been a monster to have eaten all your shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this to Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you deliver some ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she actually come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Big Bro said she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline always helps those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order some shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but it's all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise me toward the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline always helps those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Don't I look great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to say "cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to hit your back?{choking on balls... how gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, do you make fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Fireworks are like art to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love sitting and watching everyone's expressions at the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,right before we shoot off the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I set off the fireworks, everyone around starts to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing a smile to their faces is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Making people smile is... amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's just about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait till you see my huge fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, what's with that outfit? Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!{sensei... is he tutoring the guy?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing a smile to their faces is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing! Truly amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, it was a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there's a surprise for you coming in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon! Where's the watermelon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Kanji! They invited us over, so at least show some manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle's getting it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta smack it open first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we seriously gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't it sound like fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna do it too!{i'd do you, too... yukiko}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The splattering fruit juice! Bursts of joy! One night of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That bittersweetness of those days is the essence of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the essence of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's a lot of shoes! How many people are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split the watermelon open!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. It never occurred to me you'd want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, let's do it properly sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll do it right - at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds good! But I think it'll have to wait until next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you play with me again next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gotta love watermelons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelons are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing all summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to grant their wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put everyone out!{everyone's gonna put out for MC}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't the two of us go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'm glad I met you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.03,0:24:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Neo Featherman!
